org.opengis.cite.securityclient10.httpServer

Class UnifiedEndPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opengis.cite.securityclient10.httpServer.UnifiedEndPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, org.opengis.cite.jetty.io.EndPoint

    public class UnifiedEndPoint
extends Object
implements org.opengis.cite.jetty.io.EndPoint
    Subclass of EndPoint for reading the first few bytes of a client connection to determine if it is a TLS handshake (HTTPS enabled) or not (HTTP only). Source: https://stackoverflow.com/a/40076056/237958
